OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1782391699
OL,3,CKhan: Grooming gangs inquiry focus on
OL,4,CLondon must leave 'no stone unturned'
OL,6,FThe Mayor of London welcomed the
OL,7,Fgrooming gangs inquiry's focus on
OL,8,FLondon, saying "marking your own
OL,9,Fhomework is not good enough".
OL,11,FSir Sadiq Khan said it was important
OL,12,F"no stone is left unturned" as the
OL,13,Finquiry sets about its work.
OL,15,FThe Labour mayor previously came under
OL,16,Ffire for suggesting there was no
OL,17,Findication of rape gangs operating in
OL,18,Fthe capital and that the issue in
OL,19,FLondon was different from other areas.
OL,26,@pD@POUqD@\O]tD@AOUtD@[O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
