OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1782391699
OL,3,CKhan: Grooming gangs inquiry focus on
OL,4,CLondon must leave 'no stone unturned'
OL,6,FLondon is among three areas, including
OL,7,FOldham in Greater Manchester and
OL,8,FBradford and Keighley in West
OL,9,FYorkshire, to be subject to local
OL,10,Finvestigations.
OL,12,FIn its announcement on Wednesday, the
OL,13,Finquiry said it will look "in detail
OL,14,Fat what happened in a specific place `
OL,15,Fincluding how children were identified
OL,16,Fand protected, how organisations
OL,17,Fresponded, how victims were treated,
OL,18,Fand what needs to change".
OL,26,@uD@[OUzD@YO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1782391699
OL,3,CKhan: Grooming gangs inquiry focus on
OL,4,CLondon must leave 'no stone unturned'
OL,6,FOn a visit to a school in east London
OL,7,Fon Wednesday as the announcement was
OL,8,Fmade, he said: "It's really important
OL,9,Fthat we have the victims and survivors
OL,10,Fat the fore of our minds and that's
OL,11,Fone of the reasons why marking your
OL,12,Fown homework is not good enough."
OL,14,FHe added he had commissioned HM
OL,15,FInspectorate of Constabulary and Fire
OL,16,F& Rescue Services (HMICFRS) to look
OL,17,Finto the Metropolitan Police over its
OL,18,Fhandling of child sexual abuse.
OL,26,@pD@POUtD@aO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1782391699
OL,3,CKhan: Grooming gangs inquiry focus on
OL,4,CLondon must leave 'no stone unturned'
OL,6,FHe said: "We looked into the whole
OL,7,Fissue of child sex exploitation (CSE)
OL,8,Fand I welcome this external analysis
OL,9,Fof the Met Police Service."
OL,11,FMore police officers and staff have
OL,12,Fbeen trained to combat CSE and "huge
OL,13,Famounts into victims and survivors"
OL,14,Fhave been invested, he added.
OL,16,FSir Sadiq said: "It's really important
OL,17,Fno stone is left unturned when it
OL,18,Fcomes to ensuring the victims and
OL,19,Fsurvivors get justice and anybody
OL,20,Fresponsible for all their heinous
OL,21,Fcrimes are brought to book."
OL,26,@nD@JOUqD@[O]tD@`OUuD@cO]xD@QOU}D@\O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1782391699
OL,3,CKhan: Grooming gangs inquiry focus on
OL,4,CLondon must leave 'no stone unturned'
OL,6,FThe Metropolitan Police were going
OL,7,Fback 15 years to investigate cases and
OL,8,Fensure that victims and survivors get
OL,9,Fjustice and that there is "no
OL,10,Fperpetrator that should have been
OL,11,Fprosecuted but hasn't been".
OL,13,F"It's really important to get
OL,14,Freassurance that all things that could
OL,15,Fhave been done were done, but also
OL,16,Freassurance to victims and survivors
OL,17,Fthat they will get justice."
OL,26,@qD@[OUsD@[O]uD@AOUyD@\O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1782391699
OL,3,CKhan: Grooming gangs inquiry focus on
OL,4,CLondon must leave 'no stone unturned'
OL,6,FThe Conservative chairman of the
OL,7,FLondon Assembly Police and Crime
OL,8,FCommittee, Susan Hall, said: "The
OL,9,FLondon Assembly Police and Crime
OL,10,FCommittee is currently investigating
OL,11,Fthe extent to which these heinous
OL,12,Fgroups are operating in London.
OL,14,F"We heard how for too long, these
OL,15,Fgrooming gangs have been able to
OL,16,Foperate in London, are still prevalent
OL,17,Ftoday and continue to extend their
OL,18,Freach across the country.
OL,26,@pD@^OUvD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1782391699
OL,3,CKhan: Grooming gangs inquiry focus on
OL,4,CLondon must leave 'no stone unturned'
OL,6,F"The victim-survivors are the most
OL,7,Fimportant people in all of this, and I
OL,8,Fhope our own investigation, alongside
OL,9,Fthe national inquiry, can help them to
OL,10,Fknow they are finally being listened
OL,11,Fto."
OL,13,FIn a debate with Ms Hall in January
OL,14,Flast year, Sir Sadiq was accused of
OL,15,Favoiding questions about grooming
OL,16,Fgangs in London and said the capital
OL,17,Fhad issues with girls being exploited
OL,18,Fby gangs for county lines drug dealing.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@DO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1782391699
OL,3,CKhan: Grooming gangs inquiry focus on
OL,4,CLondon must leave 'no stone unturned'
OL,6,FHe said: "The situation in London in
OL,7,Frelation to young people being groomed
OL,8,Fis different to other parts of the
OL,9,Fcountry.
OL,11,F"What we have in London is young
OL,12,Fpeople being groomed ` to use your
OL,13,Fword, not mine ` to be used in county
OL,14,Flines in relation to sometimes..."
OL,26,@nD@JOUsD@AOUvD@bO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
