CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1782391699
OL,3,CKhan: Grooming gangs inquiry focus on
OL,4,CLondon must leave 'no stone unturned'
OL,6,FPressed further, he went on: "We do
OL,7,Fhave issues in London with young girls
OL,8,Fbeing groomed for county lines. Some
OL,9,Fof those girls are used for sex and
OL,10,Fthat is one of the reasons why I have
OL,11,Fset up things like the Lighthouse,
OL,12,Ffunded by City Hall."
